	<h2>Objective</h2>
	<p>Banelings will swarm in from all directions. You must control your marines and abilites to keep them alive. Gain points per round for each number of surviving marines.</p>

	<h2>Controls</h2>
	<ul>
		<li><strong>Mouse: </strong>Select and Drag individual Marines.</li>
		<li><strong>F key: </strong>Cast Forcefield at the cursor's locaton.</li>
		<li><strong>Spacebar: </strong>Time Warp</li>
	</ul>

